Basic Commands in CUA mode:
File:       Region:   Search/Replace:      Edit:                Emergency:
^Q    exit  ^C copy   ^FF   find forward   ^A mark all          ^H/F1 help
^O    open  ^X kill   ^L/F3 find next      ^B format paragraph  ^Z    undo
^S/F2 save  ^V paste  ^FE   regexp search  ^K kill line         ^D    abort
^P    print           ^FR   replace        ^J goto line
